issue.body:
Template used for reverse iteration in C++11 range-based for loops.

```c++
   std::vector<int> v = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
   for (auto x : reverse_iterate(v))
       std::cout << x << " ";
```

Port of core bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/10835 and port of commit bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/10193 (commit 4d4fb33fc, which in turns grab the idea from https://gist.github.com/arvidsson/7231973)

